Call for Abstracts

2009 International Conference on Applied Linguistics & Language
Teaching (ALLT)

                          April 16-18, 2009

Conference Themes :

 Second language acquisition (SLA): Theory and application
 Corpus/Corpora in Language Application & Teaching
 CALL and Web in Applied Linguistics and Language Teaching
 Cross Culture and Literature in Language Teaching
 Language testing & assessment
 Language for Specific Purposes (LSP) in Application & Teaching
 Teaching Chinese as a Second Language (TCSL): Trends and Challenges
 Translator and interpreter training theories and practices
 Educational objectives of applied English / foreign language programs
 Other relevant topics are also welcome.=20

